{"tid":1670591,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"彭博：香港警方已用 AI 科技進行人臉辨識","createTime":"2019-10-23T04:44:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-23T06:51:15.000Z","uid":134993,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"934282da073185340eedcce63135653e0b4c857a","tid":1670591,"uid":134993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T04:44:53.000Z","msg":"來自《彭博》 報導指從知情人事得知香港執法機構可使用 AI 軟件將任何影片跟警方的資料庫進行配對，但暫時未知有沒有在近月示威活動中進使用。<br />\n<br />\n消息透露警方最少 3 年前已使用了澳洲的 iOmniscient 科技，其工程人員已培訓了數十名警員使用這種技術。iOmniscient 的軟件可透過掃描閉路電視的影片，再自動將出現在影片裡的人臉及車牌跟警方數據庫進行配對，從而找出疑犯。根據知情人透露，在示威活動開始後的一次培訓中，有警方人員詢問過如何透過系統自動辨識車牌。"},{"pid":"3bffef0fb58432472dc9e0e4f59a989e2a35d237","tid":1670591,"uid":243366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T04:48:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36322aa990ed881741cc0f9b659565af72bc8b93","tid":1670591,"uid":229436,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T04:52:02.000Z","msg":"香港比依班狗搞到同新疆一樣  自己人打壓自己人 害死成個香港"},{"pid":"b8adc19c39a336184c7ab68106dc9055fa45a738","tid":1670591,"uid":242537,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T04:52:22.000Z","msg":"唔怪得要全港蒙面<br />\n屌你班垃圾香港省公安<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edc50ea046134692b55091eaee2f79532b113659","tid":1670591,"uid":235025,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T04:53:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4d71fbfd835c9ffecae5451012f6854f4c4de0a3","tid":1670591,"uid":35604,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T04:53:47.000Z","msg":"一國一制未"},{"pid":"d53bf58d2fcd777a1145c1e8b4ea19a7c975bb20","tid":1670591,"uid":228868,"like":0,"disl